0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"응, 여기까지 오는데 순식간이었네.\n오늘 의상 피팅이 끝나면 금세 완성될 것 같아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"코코로 짱만 해도\n벌써 의상이 완성됐을 때를 생각하고 있는 것 같아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"마술 종류라든지 연출이라든지\n그러고 보니 미셸이 수중탈출을 했으면 좋겠다고\n그런 것 같은데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"저번에는 미셸이 공중부양을 했으면 좋겠다고 말했던가……\n수중탈출에 공중부양…… 미셸을 입은 상태로는 절대 무리.\n아니, 안 입은 상태에서도 무리……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"아하하…… 그러네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"나원참, 코코로 때문에 곤란하네요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"그치만…… 싫지는 않은 거지?\n왜냐면 지금 미사키 짱, 즐거워 보이는걸.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"그, 그런가요……?\n……뭐, 뭐~ 즐거운 것 같기도 하고\n아닌 것 같기도 하고……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"즐기고…… 있으려나.\n저도 잘 모르겠지만……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"그, 그치만 여전히 바보 트리오는 제가 미셸인 줄은\n알아차리지 못했고, 코코로한테는 휘둘리기만 해서\n큰일인 것도 사실이네요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"아하, 아하하하……\n그래도 미사키 짱이 헬로해피의 활동을\n즐기고 있는 건 기뻐.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"마술을 테마로 만든 새로운 의상으로 하는 라이브도\n온 힘을 다해서 즐기자.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"그래요, 순수하게 즐길 수 있으면 된 거지만.\n아, 그래도 절대 공중부양이나 수중탈출 같은 건 안 할 거니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"……만약 제가 거절하면 어떻게 될까요.\n다른 멤버한테 시키지는… 않겠죠?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"우에엥…… 나한테는 하라고 해도 진짜 무리라고~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"만일 코코로가 제안한다면 둘이서 단호하게 거절하는 거예요.\n괜찮죠? 카논 씨.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"으, 응.\n그렇네, 아무래도…… 받아들일 수 없으니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"그래도 정말 코코로는 무슨 말을 꺼낼지 모르니까\n당분간은 정신을 바짝 차려야겠어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"공중부양 이상으로 어처구니없는 마술을\n생각해올 것 같아……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"kv2018-15-ep-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미사키","body":"게다가 하구미도 카오루 씨도 그 분위기에 편승해서\n하자는 방향으로 흘러가 버린다면……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"vo